---
title: Saucy Taiwanese Chicken Thighs with Bok Choy and Scallion Rice
description: Taiwanese cuisine combines an array of spices and flavours like soy, sesame oil and chili flakes. These saucy chicken thighs celebrate all of those things and more, with a side of scallion rice and crispy bok choy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saucy-taiwanese-chicken-thighs-342de045.jpg
